snippet.title: Mary Trump Makes Surprising Prediction About Donald & Ivanka
snippet.description:
Even though his time as President of the United States has come to an end — for now, at least — the legal woes of Donald Trump and the Trump Organization continue.

Following the recent indictment against the Trump Organization's CFO Allen Weisselberg, Donald Trump's niece Mary Trump has laid out her own theories on what may be coming next for the family in the eyes of the justice system. Part of her theories include a surprising prediction about who might flip and cooperate with authorities against the former President: his own daughter.

Speaking on the podcast The New Abnormal, Mary Trump makes a surprising prediction about Donald and Ivanka.

Keep watching to see Mary Trump's surprising prediction about Donald and Ivanka.
